sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant A as Mobile App
    participant API as Public API Server
    participant DB as Public Mirror DB

    U->>A: Enters email + password
    A->>API: POST /login

    API->>DB: Find app_user by email
    DB-->>API: User found / not found

    alt User found
        API->>API: Verify password hash
        alt Correct password
            API->>API: Generate auth token
            API-->>A: Login success
        else Wrong password
            API-->>A: 401 Unauthorized
        end
    else Not found
        API-->>A: 404 User not found
    end
